In an incremental project builder (or maybe other kinds of) plugin project:
  1) edit plugin.xml, and go to the Extensions page.
  2) select the builder element
  3) select the builder's "run" child in the "Extension Element Children"
  4) click on the "class" property in the Properties dialog
  5) click on the popup triangle, bringing up the "Java Attribute Page"
  6) select "Enter a name of an existing Java class"
  7) click the "Browse..." button to bring up the class name selector

The system displays an error alert:

 "Internal error
  An internal error has occurred. Argument cannot be null See error log for more 
details."
